track_notes: You can park the car at the start of the walk, the forest road is not allowed. This is a long walk to the summit and the last part is a bit difficult; at the top you must be very carefull and not subject to vertigo, there is no much room for antennas, but a vertical is ok. Must be done in summer or when snow has gone.
This track does not lead to the summit. We chessed! You can follow this track counter clockwise is better
